edu.stanford.cfuller.imageanalysistools.meta

Class AnalysisMetadataXMLParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.cfuller.imageanalysistools.meta.AnalysisMetadataParser
      • edu.stanford.cfuller.imageanalysistools.meta.AnalysisMetadataXMLParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParameterParser
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnalysisMetadataXMLWriter

    public class AnalysisMetadataXMLParser
extends AnalysisMetadataParser
    A parser for new-format XML analysis metadata files.

    If an old-format XML parameter file is passed in instead, it will be passed off to a LegacyParameterXMLParser.

    Author:
    Colin J. Fuller
